name: SportsQuiz
0:
”Alexa, launch Sports Quiz”
”is it four”
”can you repeat”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sports quiz
des: The skill asks random questions about various sports. Launch the skill by the name and answer questions by saying a number between 1 and 4. If you don't know the answer, you can skip. To hear again you can ask to repeat.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
